Package de.server.controller.goods

Class GoodsController

java.lang.Object
de.server.controller.goods.GoodsController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/goods") public class GoodsController extends Object
The class manages the goods, goods can be created, deleted, changed, and different lists can be issued.
